P.title: Will the price of Bitcoin be above $100,000 on 1st January 2025?
P.body: Resolves YES if the spot price of Bitcoin against USD is more than 100,000 on 1st January 2025. Resolves NO otherwise.

not_P.title: Will the price of Bitcoin be less than or equal to $100,000 on 1st January 2025?
not_P.body: Resolves YES if the spot price of Bitcoin against USD is more than 100,000 on 1st January 2025. Resolves NO otherwise.
